Project:
* calculate and manipulate 1D-HO solutions (C++ / armadillo)
* use git, doxygen, make, cxxtest, remark.js

Work to be done

   * implement the calculation of the 1D-HO solutions (along the zz-axis, using the recurrence relation)
   * evaluate and plot the first 1D-HO solutions (using xmgrace, matplotlib...)
   * numerically check the energy EnEnâ€‹ of the 1D-HO solutions (estimate the derivatives)
   * numerically check the orthonormality of the 1D-HO solutions (use a quadrature)
   * present your results using the remark.js template



